Package Spell

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Spell
    Interface for all spells
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ACCIO
    Spell which will grab the targeted item and pull it toward you with a force determined by your level in the spell.
    AGUAMENTI
    Spell which places a block of water against the targeted block.
    ALARTE_ASCENDARE
    Shoots target high into air.
    APARECIUM
    Spell which causes any stationary spell objects to flair with an intensity equal to your level
    AQUA_ERUCTO
    Spell shoots a block of water at a target, extinguishing fire
    ARRESTO_MOMENTUM
    Slows down any item or living entity according to your level in the spell.
    AVADA_KEDAVRA
    Does direct damage to a living entity according to your level in the spell.
    AVIS
    Transfigures bats from air
    BOMBARDA
    Creates an explosion at the target which scales with the player's level in the spell.
    BOMBARDA_MAXIMA
    Creates an explosion at the target location twice as powerful as bombarda.
    CONFUNDO
    Casts a powerful confusion potion effect on the player that scales with the caster's level in this spell.
    CRESCERE_PROTEGAT
    Grows a stationarySpellObject's radius
    DEFODIO
    Mines a line of blocks of length depending on the player's level in this spell.
    DELETRIUS
    Deletes an item entity.
    DUCKLIFORS  
    EBUBLIO
    Bubble head charm gives the player water breathing for a length of time depending on the player's spell level.
    EQUUSIFORS
    Transfigures an item into a horse.
    ET_INTERFICIAM_ANIMAM_LIGAVERIS
    Creates a horcrux stationary spell object where it collides with a block.
    EXPELLIARMUS
    Disarms an entity of it's held item, flinging the item in the direction of the caster with force determined by the spell level.
    FIANTO_DURI  
    FIENDFYRE
    Spawns other fiendfyre projectiles with a decreasing chance as the spell ages.
    FRANGE_LIGNEA
    Bursts a log into a stack of coreless wands, whose number depends on the player's spell level.
    GEMINIO
    Produces a second item exactly like the first item
    HORREAT_PROTEGAT
    Shrinks a stationarySpellProjectile's radius
    IMMOBULUS
    Immobilizes a player for an amount of time depending on the player's spell level.
    IMPEDIMENTA
    Slows any living entity by an amount and time depending on the player's spell level.
    INCENDIO
    Sets fire to blocks.
    INFORMOUS
    Gives information on LivingEntity (health) and StationarySpellObj (duration)
    LIGATIS_COR
    If a coreless wand is near enough a core material, makes a wand of the wand wood type and core type.
    LUMOS
    Gives nightvision for an amount of time depending on the player's spell level.
    MUFFLIATO
    Creates a muffliato stationary spell object.
    OBLIVIATE
    Decreases all of target player's spell levels by the caster's level in obliviate.
    PROTEGO_HORRIBILIS  
    PROTEGO_TOTALUM
    Creates a PROTEGO_TOTALUM Stationary Spell Object
    REDUCTO
    Creates an explosion of magnitude depending on the spell level which destroys blocks and sets fires.
    REPARIFARGE  
    REPARO
    Repairs an itemstack you aim it at.
    SILENCIO
    Silences a player for a duration depending on the spell's level.
    SPONGIFY
    Creates a spongify StationarySpellObj
    STUPEFY
    Blinds and slows the target entity for a duration depending on the spell's level.
